## 1. PLATFORM OVERVIEW

Fourthwall is a creator commerce and membership platform. Single branded storefront at a custom domain. Acts as **Merchant of Record** — collects and remits sales tax globally.

```
COVERS      Merch · Memberships · Donations · Digital products · Sales channels
IS NOT      Discovery platform · Per-creation billing model
PRO PLAN    $19/mo — removes 5% fee on digital products only
```

Core fees `⚠️ C12`:

| Component | Free Plan | Pro ($19/mo) |
|---|---|---|
| Memberships | 5% | 5% |
| Digital products | 5% | 0% |
| Physical products | 0% | 0% |
| CC processing | 2.9% + $0.30 | same |
| PayPal | 3.49% + $0.49 | same |

---

## 2. AUTHENTICATION

For single-shop automation: **Basic Auth only**. OAuth is invite-only and not needed.

### Basic Auth (API Key) `✓`

```
WHERE    https://my-shop.fourthwall.com/admin/dashboard/settings/for-developers
ROLE     SUPER ADMIN required (shop owner = SUPER ADMIN by default)
```

```bash
curl -u "your_username:your_password" \
  https://api.fourthwall.com/open-api/v1.0/shops/current
```

```javascript
const base64 = btoa("your_username:your_password");
fetch("https://api.fourthwall.com/open-api/v1.0/shops/current", {
  headers: { "Authorization": `Basic ${base64}` }
});
```

### Storefront Token (read-only public data)

```
FORMAT    ptkn_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
PASSED AS ?storefront_token=YOUR_TOKEN  (query param)
SCOPE     Public product data only. Safe for client-side use.
```

---

## 3. API SURFACE

```
RATE LIMIT    100 requests / 10-second rolling window
BEHAVIOR      Excess requests DELAYED, not rejected (no 429)
```

| API | Base URL | Auth | Prefix |
|---|---|---|---|
| Platform | `https://api.fourthwall.com` | Basic Auth | `/open-api/v1.0/` |
| Memberships | `https://api.fourthwall.com` | Basic Auth | `/open-api/v1.1/memberships/` |
| Storefront | `https://storefront-api.fourthwall.com` | Storefront token | `/v1/` |

### Key Platform Endpoints

```
GET    /open-api/v1.0/shops/current            ✓
GET    /open-api/v1.0/orders
GET    /open-api/v1.0/orders/{id}
GET    /open-api/v1.0/products
GET    /open-api/v1.0/supporters
GET    /open-api/v1.0/subscriptions
POST   /open-api/v1.0/webhooks                 ✓
GET    /open-api/v1.0/webhooks
PUT    /open-api/v1.0/webhooks/{id}
DELETE /open-api/v1.0/webhooks/{id}
```

### Key Storefront Endpoints

```
Base: https://storefront-api.fourthwall.com/v1
Auth: ?storefront_token=TOKEN on every request

GET  /v1/collections/all/products    ← no list-all endpoint — use 'all' collection
GET  /v1/products/{product_slug}
POST /v1/carts                       body: { "currency": "USD" }
POST /v1/carts/{cart_id}/items       body: { "variantId": "...", "quantity": 1 }
GET  /v1/carts/{cart_id}
```

Checkout redirect: `https://{shop}.fourthwall.com/checkout/?cartCurrency=USD&cartId={cart_id}`

Cart uses `variantId` (not product ID). Payments cannot go through API — always redirect to hosted checkout.

### Memberships Posts Endpoint `✓`

```
GET /open-api/v1.1/memberships/posts

Required: state = Published | Scheduled | All   (see C9)
Optional: page · limit · search_query · types[] · tags_ids[]
```

Access control object on every post:
```json
{
  "access": {
    "type": "Public | FreeMembers | FreeAndPaidMembers | MembersOnly | Plans",
    "tiers": [{ "id": 123 }]
  }
}
```

