## 6. MEMBERSHIPS — SYSTEM MODEL

### Core Components

**Tiers** — pricing levels. At minimum one tier required to launch. Define: price, billing cadence, perks, trial options.

**Perks** — actual reasons someone joins:
- Custom perk (most flexible — promises, entitlements, AMAs, VIP)
- Discord role assignment
- Members-only discounts
- Members-only products
- Private audio RSS feed

**Free tier** — set price to $0. All free accounts auto-assigned. Supports custom perks only — no Discord or advanced perks.

**Member lifecycle states:**
```
Free account · Free tier member · Free trial member
Paid active member · Expiring member · Former member
```

### Discord Perk Setup `✓`

```
1. Create roles in Discord server
2. Dashboard → Apps → Discord → Connect
3. Assign Discord perk to each tier
4. Fourthwall bot joins server — must retain permission to manage assigned roles
5. Members authenticate at /supporters/perks
6. Bot assigns role automatically
```

> ⚠️ If Fourthwall bot loses role-management permission, the entire system breaks silently.

### Discounts & Promos

- **7-day free trial** — first-time members only; former members cannot reuse
- **Intro pricing** — automatic for launch period, first billing period only
- **Promo codes** — Promotions → Create promotion → Membership promo
- **Twitch subscriber discounts** — max 80% off; reverts if sub lapses
- **Limitation:** discounts only apply to one billing period

### Direct Messages & Locked Messages (PPV)

**DMs** — one-to-one. Target: all members, selected tiers, expiring/former members, free accounts. Enable: Memberships → Settings → Messages.

**Tips in DMs** — configure minimum ($1–$100) to reduce spam.

**Locked messages** — PPV DMs. Price: $1–$100. Former members can unlock but cannot reply without rejoining. Audio/video processing up to 1 hour. Edit/delete after sending not supported.

### Annual Subscriptions

Enable: Memberships → Settings → General. Improves cash flow and retention. Fourthwall auto-calculates yearly total.

### Membership Badges

**Streak badge** — default, duration-based. "New member" → "X-month member." Customize per streak length.

**Custom badges** — define by tier, comments, likes given/received, or manual. Text, icon, border/bg/text colors configurable. Custom icon upload not yet supported.

### Mobile App (PWA)

Auto-available when Memberships is enabled. Not on App Store/Google Play — install via browser.

Push notifications: Android + iOS 16.4+. No background video playback, no PiP, tablets not supported.

### Known Limitations

- Custom badge icon upload not yet supported
- Edit/delete for sent DMs/locked messages not supported
- Multi-month/multi-year discounts not supported
- Promo usage caps not yet available
- Free tiers support custom perks only
- Mobile app cannot be disabled in self-serve settings

