## 7. EMAIL & NEWSLETTER

Fourthwall does **not** send newsletter emails natively. Options:

| Tool | Integration type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Klaviyo | Native sync | Full transactional + campaigns |
| Mailchimp | Native sync | Standard email marketing |
| beehiiv | Native sync | Newsletter-focused |
| Kite | Native sync | — |
| Laylo | Native sync | — |
| Zapier | No-code | Works with any tool |

Once connected, new contacts sync automatically. Older contacts: download CSV from Settings → General → Email marketing → export.

**What Fourthwall does send automatically (non-customizable without integration):**
- Order confirmations
- Shipping notifications
- Abandoned cart reminders
- Thank-you emails (cannot be customized or disabled)

