## 8. PLATFORM INTEGRATIONS — WHAT'S ACTUALLY POSSIBLE

| Platform | Status | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| **StreamElements** | ✓ Native | Apps → Alerts |
| **Streamlabs** | ✓ Native | Uses "Tips" event type (renamed from Donations) |
| **Discord** | ✓ Native | Apps → Discord |
| **YouTube Product Shelf** | ✓ Native | Products surfaced on channel page |
| **TikTok Shop** | ✓ Native | — |
| **Printful** | ✓ Native | Auto-fulfillment; to migrate existing designs, submit request form |
| **Zapier** | ✓ No-code | 12 triggers, 4 actions |
| **WordPress / Wix / Hostinger** | ⚠️ Link-out only | No plugin; use "Buy Now" links or per-page iframe embeds. Full cart/checkout always redirects to Fourthwall |
| **Shopify** | ✗ No integration | Migrate fully or link out only |
| **Printify** | ✗ Not supported | No native integration |

> Fourthwall is its own full platform — no deep embedding in third-party CMSes. Linking out is the recommended pattern.

