## 11. LAUNCH CHECKLIST

### Memberships Minimum Viable Launch

- [ ] 1 paid tier created with 1–3 clear perks
- [ ] Welcome post created
- [ ] 1 public post live
- [ ] Memberships added to homepage and menu
- [ ] Annual plan enabled
- [ ] Launch discount or promo code ready
- [ ] Discord perk configured (bot has role-management permission)
- [ ] Member-only product or discount configured

### Streaming Integration

- [ ] Webhook endpoint deployed and tested
- [ ] Signature verification live (`X-Fourthwall-Hmac-SHA256`)
- [ ] Test event fired from Dashboard → Webhooks → Send test notification
- [ ] StreamElements connected (Apps → Alerts → StreamElements)
- [ ] Purchase alert fires for `ORDER_PLACED` and `DONATION`
- [ ] Membership variation alert configured with `-1` amount condition
- [ ] Discord native integration enabled or custom bot handling role assignment

### Merch Production

- [ ] Master canvas at 15,000 × 9,000px, 300 PPI, RGB
- [ ] Sublimation colors pushed +10–15% brightness/saturation
- [ ] Files named per convention
- [ ] Layered source file preserved in Source/

